public abstract class WriteRequest extends DurableRequest
Represents a base class for the single row modifying operations NoSQLHandle.put(oracle.nosql.driver.ops.PutRequest) and NoSQLHandle.delete(oracle.nosql.driver.ops.DeleteRequest).
